data.title: It I II III IV Syllabus 07-11-07
data.meta_description:
It i II III IV Syllabus 07-11-07 - Free download as Word Doc (.doc), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document provides the course structure for the first year of a Bachelor of Technology in Information Technology degree. It includes 14 subjects divided between theory, tutorial, and practical components. The total credits for the year are 104. 

The subjects cover areas like English, mathematics, physics, programming, electronics, and communication skills. For each subject, the document lists the course code, name, theory hours, tutorial hours, and credits awarded. It also provides the total credits and hours for the year.
